---
title: Fruity Beef Curry with coriander and green beans
description: Fruitiness and curry may not be two concepts you would immediately put together, but in fact, they're a flavour pairing that really works! The fruitiness in this recipe comes from a helping of cranberry chutney, which also adds a pleasing sweetness to the dish.
